#. type: delimited block =
#: /mnt/c/Users/etrees/Desktop/private/spring-framework/origin/framework-docs/modules/ROOT/pages/core/beans/factory-scopes.adoc:500
msgid ""
"CGLIB proxies do not intercept private methods. Attempting to call a private "
